    "title": "Principal Frontend Developer at SAP India Capital India",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Frontend Developer looking for your next big career move? SAP India Capital India in Raipur offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout SAP India Capital India:\nSAP India Capital India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with SAP India Capital India!",
